{{Wiktionary}} '''Cinema''' may refer to: {{TOC right}}
==Film== * [[Cinematography]], the science or art of motion-picture photography * [[Film]] or movie, a series of still images that create the illusion of a moving image ** [[Film industry]], the technological and commercial institutions of filmmaking ** [[Filmmaking]], the process of making a film * [[Movie theater]] (also called a cinema), a building in which films are shown * [[Cinema (2008 film)|''Cinema'' (2008 film)]] or ''Bommalattam'', a Tamil film directed by Bharathiraja
==Music== ===Bands=== * [[Cinema (band)]], a band formed in 1982 by ex-Yes members Alan White and Chris Squire * [[The Cinema]], an American indie pop band
